-- French Cyclist Riblon Wins Tour de France Stage to Alpe d’Huez
-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 2013-07-18T15:22:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-18/french-cyclist-riblon-wins-tour-de-france-stage-to-alpe-d-huez.html
Christophe Riblon won stage 18 of
the Tour de  France , which finished atop the Alpe d’Huez
mountain. The AG2R-La Mondiale rider is the first French stage
winner at the centenary edition of the race.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
